^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Let me discuss 2 things here. First, when to bid 3S vs 4S with 3 card support when pard opens a weak-2. By the law of total tricks, you always should bid at least 3 with 3 cards support (9  card fit). However, on this hand I had 19 HCP, so even with a minimum weak-2, we have enough points for game. Therefore, 4S was clear.|
