NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|With say 15 or 16 points, I would use the Ogust 2N bid. After a 2NT (Ogust bid), partner would bid 3H or 3S with 8-10, so with 15 I would go to 4. But the more important rule is, if pard opens a weak-2, always raise to 3 at least with 3 card support.|
